<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.100.112458.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Habitats of Tulostoma species in Hungary: a T. hungaricum in Orgovany b T. sacchariolens in Orgovany c T. dunense in Izsak (Soltszentimre) d T. shaihuludii in Izsak (Soltszentimre). Photos: P. Finy." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/944689" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.100.112458.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Tulostoma hungaricum: a, c-g FP- 2021 - 01 - 24 a (BP 112641, holotype), Bocsa b FP- 2019 - 11 - 23, Orgovany a-c basidiocarps d, e basidiospores f, g capillitium with basidiospores. Scale bars: 1 µm (d); 10 µm (e); 20 µm (f, g). Photos: a, b, e-g P. Finy c L. Albert d K. Boka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/944692" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

